In 1985, a man was murdered and the case was never solved.  
Fifty years later, a powerful US Senator pressures the Historical Event Research Organization (HERO) to investigate the murder, using newly-developed Time Travel technology.    
An Army Ranger captain is selected to travel back in time and witness the event.  
Once there, he meets a beautiful woman, which disrupts the ancestry of his best friend.   
He is captivated by the woman and must overcome his emotions and his heart to complete his mission and repair the damage to history he has inadvertently caused. 

